summary: Tony: [ To Carol ] C'mon on, Cap. The war thing isn't the problem. The military work's keeping you and Rhodey apart. You two...
body:
Tony: [ To Carol ] C'mon on, Cap. The war thing isn’t the problem. The military work’s keeping you and Rhodey apart. You two just need to bone.

Peter: [ Whimpers ].

Carol: …What did he say?

Peter: [ Whispering ] Don’t say it again.

Tony: I said you two need to bone.

Peter: [ Gulps]

Carol: How… dare you, Iron man? I am yOUR SUPERIOR AVENGEEEER!

Carol: [Shouting from the door] BONE!

Carol: What happens in my bedroom, Mr. Stark, is none of your business!

Carol: [ Shouting from the door again] BONE?!

Carol: [ At Tony] Don’t ever speak to me like that again.
